                </div>
                <div class='contact-box contact-box-3'>
                    <p class='p'>Value Advisors Spółka z o.o. Sp. k.</p>
                    <p class='p'><strong>NIP: 9522062080</strong></p>
                    <p class='p'><strong>REGON: 141697836</strong></p>
